for Dr. Chamberlain, because
the Affordable Care Act,

00:23:55.920 --> 00:23:58.180
especially for kids and
especially for folks

00:23:58.180 --> 00:24:00.720
with disabilities is a life saver.

00:24:00.720 --> 00:24:04.050
It means no annual caps, no lifetime caps,

00:24:04.050 --> 00:24:06.160
and you couldn't be discriminated on with

00:24:06.160 --> 00:24:09.430
buying health insurance
because of that disability.

00:24:09.430 --> 00:24:10.890
That was important.

00:24:10.890 --> 00:24:13.640
It's important to our
patients, and we will continue

00:24:13.640 --> 00:24:15.173
to strongly advocate for that.

00:24:16.800 --> 00:24:18.742
The future of Medicaid, the challenges,

00:24:18.742 --> 00:24:20.500
Amy touched on some.

