Make no mistake, if you do block grants

00:24:34.470 --> 00:24:36.610
or per capita, it's cutting funding

00:24:36.610 --> 00:24:38.900
because then they put it in a block grant,

00:24:38.900 --> 00:24:41.743
they don't see anybody's
face, and then they cut.

00:24:42.970 --> 00:24:47.030
And most serious again, is a
non-realistic understanding

00:24:47.030 --> 00:24:51.003
