So we get stories all the time.

00:40:52.680 --> 00:40:56.900
It is a way for the physicians
and the caregivers to vent,

00:40:56.900 --> 00:40:59.620
to put their story down, to
share what they're seeing.

00:40:59.620 --> 00:41:02.710
We have tons and tons and daily examples

00:41:02.710 --> 00:41:04.480
of people delaying coming in because

00:41:04.480 --> 00:41:06.450
of fear of immigration.

00:41:06.450 --> 00:41:09.960
We have people who
delayed, the worst is a kid

00:41:09.960 --> 00:41:12.485
who got delayed getting a
really important diagnosis

00:41:12.485 --> 00:41:15.750
that probably changed his course.

